{"tid":130231,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"［求接收］有幾部未砌MG","createTime":"2017-02-22T09:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T01:11:59.000Z","uid":44517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"473d297b13f884c0ea8092334c10bce2310b1a77","tid":130231,"uid":44517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:00:47.000Z","msg":"事件起源2015年巴巴托斯第一季迷住左我<br />\n我就每出一隻1/144我都買，真係好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為2016新年感謝祭既活動變相我有好多卡係手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住就中左3獎<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/22/160218_90803ef9be1cb53c0ac1115c79d5dd76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F22%2F160218_90803ef9be1cb53c0ac1115c79d5dd76.jpg&h=1c11b806&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問題嚟喇，我真係好唔鐘意砌MG<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，如果鐵血系列都算，砌MG好痛苦，我完全無時間砌加唔想砌，我寧願砌hg輕輕鬆鬆又方便擺唔阻住啲位置。<br />\n結果我由上年4月好開心拎返屋企變放左係到，到而家都無掂過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總共七部想出讓，求巴打接手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有巴打係完美主義者千其唔好入嚟，我啲盒可能有啲塵，當然我會抹，仲有啲盒無封口，我拎個時就係咁，如果怕少左件你都可以返出去，我無開過所以我都唔知，我只保證到無開過盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以百無禁忌的你先好入黎傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有興趣請入我telegram group, <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAD_FI4NenH5I3yhRYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAD_FI4NenH5I3yhRYA&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8Ci7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=03fab028\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAD_FI4NenH5I3yhRYA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d8dd352c61a01da5af5af77dd4fb4e5f0dcba4c","tid":130231,"uid":44223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:02:35.000Z","msg":"巴打你個個好似係channel黎我地講唔到嘢"},{"pid":"f14659812a8b3c12bebb18fd3bca94d9f57d7de5","tid":130231,"uid":44223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:03:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你個個好似係channel黎我地講唔到嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Fhin5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFhin5&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8Ci7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=7d52772c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Fhin5</a><br />\n<br />\nbtw有興趣要"},{"pid":"d035302d02d3be11d7638bc8ee4402c64d031a54","tid":130231,"uid":44223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:04:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打你個個好似係channel黎我地講唔到嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Fhin5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFhin5&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8Ci7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=7d52772c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Fhin5</a><br />\n<br />\nbtw有興趣要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係秒入個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593d61be19748b5dc0c94a76a8b6d4281dbdb169","tid":130231,"uid":44517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T09:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打你個個好似係channel黎我地講唔到嘢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Fhin5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FFhin5&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8Ci7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=7d52772c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Fhin5</a><br />\n<br />\nbtw有興趣要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係秒入個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識唔識點set<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"